We currently run with Django from SVN:
http://code.djangoproject.com/svn/django/trunk/django
r7602

Currently upgrading to work with r8055

Download tinymce and extract it into a directory called trunk/deme_django/static/javascripts/tinymce
Download an iconset called crystal project (at everaldo) and extract the size folders to a folder called trunk/deme_django/static/crystal_project
sudo apt-get install graphviz (for gen_graph.py support)
